# isEqual(to:)

**Instance Method**

Indicates whether the indexes in the receiving index set are the same indexes contained in another index set.

## Declaration

```swift
func isEqual(to indexSet: IndexSet) -> Bool
```

## Parameters

- **indexSet**: Index set being inquired about.

## Return Value

[doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true] when the indexes in the receiving index set are the same indexes `indexSet` contains, [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/false] otherwise.
